text: Kamal Haider is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Narsingdi-3. ==Career== Haider was elected to parliament from Narsingdi-3 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Kamal Haider (politician)
